  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>In response to a weapon attack or Bukijutsu being made towards you, you spring forth black rods from your skin to stop the weapon in its path. You gain a +5 bonus to AC against the triggering attack. If this causes the attack to miss, the attacking creature spends the rest of its action pulling its weapon from your rods, making no additional attacks as part of that action, even if they would usually get multiple.</p>",
